{
  "id": "CHAR_danel_vossik",
  "label": "Danel Vossik",
  "description": "A lean young adult of human stock, bearing light skin marked by wind-chap across the cheeks and a long-healed cut at the right brow. Blue eyes sit deep under straight brows, giving the face an intent, forward-looking cast. Blonde hair is worn in a messy2 fall that frames an angular jaw and prominent cheekbones. The hands show early callus at the palms and fingers, consistent with steady travel and habitual gear-handling.",
  "short_description": "young male traveler",
