    "skinTone": "light",
    "personality": "Restless and purposeful, this newcomer measures life by roads taken and risks accepted, treating each encounter as a test of character and competence. He pursues adventure as a disciplined search for meaning, preferring direct action and honest bargains over idle talk. He maintains a practical optimism that survives hardship and keeps him moving when others settle.",
    "race": "human",
    "messages": [
      {
        "role": "user",
        "action": "input",
        "opts": {
          "text": "I look around."
        },
        "date": "999.M1 05:57",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false
      },
      {
        "date": "999.M1 05:59",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false,
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "narration",
        "opts": {
          "text": "Dawn’s clouded light lies dull on the soot-dark plating; tether rings stud the cinder-scoured deck, low bulwarks hem the edge, and braced rigging and cable-stays hum faintly with a prickling electrostatic charge, shuttered lantern housings giving only a grudging gray. Near the helm the lean helmsman keeps the ship steady with both hands, the broad-shouldered captain stands watchful a few paces off like a verdict, and a young traveler lingers by the lash points and hatch coamings, eyes roaming as if measuring who belongs."
        }
      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "action": "input",
        "opts": {
          "text": "I look around."
        },
        "date": "999.M1 06:00",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false
      },
      {
        "date": "999.M1 06:02",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false,
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "narration",
        "opts": {
          "text": "Cloudy dawn leaks a flat gray light over ash-scored planking, tether rings, low bulwarks, soot-dark plating, shuttered lanterns, and cable-braced rigging on iron-banded spars; beyond the rail, violet storm-glare stains the horizon like a bruise that won’t confess. Two young travelers linger near the weathered rail, the helmsman stands braced at the wheel like it owes him money, and the captain paces with the proprietorial impatience of a man supervising the concept of safety; from here no obvious gangplank or easy exit shows, and everything looks cinched down for hard weather."
        }
      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "action": "input",
        "opts": {
          "text": "I do a complex dance"
        },
        "date": "999.M1 06:03",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false
      },
      {
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "milestone",
        "opts": {
          "type": "skill_check",
          "label": "⚔ Perform a complex dance on the deck.",
          "subtext": "Success!",
          "entityId": null,
          "checkDetail": {
            "type": "standard",
            "stat": "dexterity",
            "statValue": 50,
            "roll": 16,
            "modifier": 20,
            "target": 70
          },
          "combatData": null
        },
        "date": null,
        "omitFromTranscript": true,
        "hidden": false
      },
      {
        "date": "999.M1 06:08",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false,
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "narration",
        "opts": {
          "text": "Flat gray dawn watches in judgment as the ship rolls underfoot; the routine threads between tether rings and bulwark with irritating competence, ending cleanly without so much as a toe to the wrong plank. The two young travelers blink, then grin at each other like they’ve just been handed a free scandal, while the helmsman flicks a quick approving glance and keeps the wheel like it’s a religious obligation; the captain’s pacing stutters, offended that grace has occurred without permits."
        }
      },
      {
        "date": "999.M1 06:08",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false,
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "dialog",
        "opts": {
          "characterId": "CHAR_danel_vossik",
          "text": "Well. That’s one way to keep warm without paying for rum."
        }
      },
      {
        "date": "999.M1 06:08",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false,
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "dialog",
        "opts": {
          "characterId": "CHAR_severan_dusk",
          "text": "Good footwork. Don’t do it near the lines."
        }
      },
      {
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "dialog",
        "opts": {
          "characterId": "CHAR_kael_orsino",
          "text": "If the storm takes us, at least we’ll die cultured."
        },
        "date": "999.M1 06:08",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false
      },
      {
        "role": "assistant",
        "action": "dialog",
        "opts": {
          "characterId": "CHAR_severin_drach",
          "text": "Marvelous. Now, unless that dance is rated for rigging maintenance, kindly keep your heroics where they don’t tempt the sea to notice us."
        },
        "date": "999.M1 06:08",
        "omitFromTranscript": false,
        "hidden": false
      },
